—$75 million for economic recovery programs in Nicaragua, to be sought as an
                        FY 1980 Economic Support Fund supplemental
                    authorization and appropriation;

—$10 million in Foreign Military Sales credits to Eastern Caribbean countries,
                    for the planned joint coast guard and other purposes, to be provided through
                    reprogramming of FY 1980 FMS funds on a worldwide basis;
